data.description:
Luxurious 4 Bedroom Home with Prime Location! $5,000 Carpet Allowance! ADDITIONAL $5,000 grant when using preferred lender! Total of $10,000 at closing!

Welcome to your dream home! This magnificent 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom house is a true gem that offers spacious living areas and remarkable features that surpass the rest. Nestled on a corner lot in a beautiful neighborhood, this home is twice as big as most houses in the area, providing you with unparalleled space and comfort.

As you step inside, you'll be greeted by two generous living areas, perfect for entertaining guests or spending quality time with your loved ones. The formal dining room exudes elegance and is ideal for hosting memorable dinners. Prepare to be amazed by the huge extra hidden storage in the garage, which is so extensive it could easily be counted as a 2.5 car garage. 

Formerly a parsonage, this home has been meticulously cared for and updated. The north side features brand-new windows that invite natural light to illuminate the interior. The roof is just one year old, providing peace of mind and ensuring years of worry-free living.

Location, location, location! This residence is perfectly situated, backing up to the renowned Booker T. Washington High School. As a resident, you will have the privilege of enjoying a view of the football field right from your backyard. Additionally, you'll be only one house away from the prestigious KIPP Charter School.

The neighborhood has many amenities for families. Just a couple of blocks away, you'll discover two fantastic parks: Wheeling Park and B.C. Franklin Park. These parks boast multiple playgrounds, basketball courts, picnic areas, and even a splash pad, providing endless recreational opportunities for everyone

Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a home that exceeds all expectations. Call now to schedule a showing!
